OL,5, A woman left struggling with thousands 
OL,6, of pounds of debt after escaping a     
OL,7, violent partner feared getting help    
OL,8, would allow him to find her.           
OL,10,FHelen - not her real name - realised   
OL,11,Fgetting her #10,000 debt written off   
OL,12,Fmeant her address being published on a 
OL,13,Fregister of people unable to pay.      
OL,15,F"If he could get his hands on me, he   
OL,16,Fwould kill me," she said.              
OL,18,FAfter advice, Helen stopped this from  
OL,19,Fhappening and has urged others in      
OL,20,Fsimilar situations to seek help too.   
